<p>注意：请确保你会使用Micro G，如果不会，请查看<a class="link"   href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMTQ1MDMxNg==&mid=2247484159&idx=1&sn=7c0018028b6803590bc8a3735baf1ea7&chksm=c26b9e5cf51c174aa80993914658f0a7b9841c8232e4c668cff7fee50eaed1dccbe8f8827f0f#rd" >推文 <i class="fa-regular fa-arrow-up-right-from-square fa-sm"></i></a></p>
